<div class="newsletter-capture">
  <div class="newsletter-content">
    <h3>🔥 Alerta de Derrumbe de Precios</h3>
    <p>Los precios en Mercado Libre suben y bajan de madrugada. Dejanos tu email y te avisamos (sin hacer spam) cuando nuestro bot detecte una oferta brutal real en tecnología.</p>
    <form class="newsletter-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('¡Gracias por suscribirte al radar de precios VASTTO!')">
      <input type="email" placeholder="Tu mejor email..." required />
      <button type="submit">Rastrear Ofertas</button>
    </form>
    <small>🔒 Tu mail está seguro. Odiamos el spam tanto como vos.</small>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .newsletter-capture {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827 0%, #1f2937 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
    color: #f3f4f6;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid #374151;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .newsletter-capture::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50px;
    right: -50px;
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    background: #6c47ff;
    filter: blur(80px);
    opacity: 0.5;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  
  .newsletter-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .newsletter-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: #fff;
  }
  
  .newsletter-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #9ca3af;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .newsletter-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .newsletter-form input {
    flex-grow: 1;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #4b5563;
    background: #374151;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1rem;
    outline: none;
  }
  
  .newsletter-form input:focus {
    border-color: #6c47ff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(108, 71, 255, 0.2);
  }
  
  .newsletter-form button {
    background: #6c47ff;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  
  .newsletter-form button:hover {
    background: #5535e0;
  }
  
  .newsletter-content small {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .newsletter-form {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
